sellerAgent.name: Shelly Salas Your Home Sold Guaranteed

data.description:
Your Dream Home with Private Pool Awaits!
This remarkable property offers a perfect blend of modern elegance and comfortable living. Step inside, and discover a beautifully designed and spacious interior. The living area is illuminated by natural light, creating an open and inviting atmosphere. Your kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances, sleek granite countertops, and a walk-in pantry. The master bedroom is complete with an ensuite bathroom that exudes spa-like luxury. It features a glass-enclosed shower adorned with stunning tile work, and offers dual sinks for added convenience. Your backyard is a private paradise! The sparkling pool invites you to relax, or host unforgettable parties with family and friends. The 2-story pool house is a delightful addition offering endless possibilities. You can also look forward to significant cost savings on energy, thanks to the solar panel system that is included with the home! Don't miss this opportunity– Contact us today to schedule a tour!
